019 as the third single from Tones and I's debut EP ''[[The Kids Are Coming]]''. Upon release Tones and I said \"[It's] about people who live the same repetitive life in fear of failure. So, they never try.\"<ref name=\"FirstSpin\">{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/triplej/news/musicnews/tones-and-i-new-song-never-seen-rain-debut-ep-kids-are-coming/11312586|title=First Spin: Tones And I continues winning streak with 'Never Seen The Rain'|publisher=ABC|date=16 July 2019 |accessdate=18 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://musicfeeds.com.au/news/listen-to-a-new-song-from-tones-and-i-never-seen-the-rain/|title= Listen To A New Song From Tones And I, \u2018Never Seen The Rain\u2019|publisher=Music Feeds|date=16 July 2019|accessdate=20 July 2019}}</ref> \nIn January 2020, the single was released outside of Australia. In February, it achieved gold status in New Zealand.\n\n==Critical reception==\nAl Newstead from ABC said \"'Never Seen the Rain' retains her keen pop sensibilities but wraps those distinctive vocals into an uplifting chorus.\"<ref name=\"FirstSpin\"/>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video was produced by Visible Studios, directed by Nick Kozakis and Liam Kelly, and released on 7 August 2019.\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from [[AllMusic]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/never-seen-the-rain-mw0003309292/credits|title=Never Seen The Rain - Tones and I|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=16 October 2019}}</ref>\n\n* [[Tones and I|Toni Watson]] \u2013 composer\n* [[Konstantin Kersting]] \u2013 mixing, production\n* Andrei Eremin \u2013 mastering\n\n==Charts==\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|7|artist=Tones and I|song=Never Seen the Rain|rowheader=true|accessdate=8 January 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|70|artist=Tones and I|song=Never Seen the Rain|rowheader